public class LSPModifier
extends LSPObject

Represents a "modifier" as defined in the STARTS 1.0 specification. Modifiers are used inside of terms (LSPTerm), and also in some metadata. See the ModifierNames class for legal names and codes.

Note that these modifiers come from the basic1 set.
